<content type="str">Movies News / Jon Galt We are bringing you our top 10 Christmas 2013 movie releases 

We have already given you some interesting films that are coming out 

Today we move on to number six on the list 

So, after a brief break, we are back with our top 10 Christmas 2013 movie releases and we have another interesting choice for you. So far in our list we have had a look at some exciting movies, including American Hustle last time out, and today, we move on to number six on the list. 

Ben Stiller stars in The Secret Life of Walter Mitty 

Some of you will already know a fair amount about the upcoming movie The Secret Life of Walter Mitty, as there has been plenty of promotional material on the movie, not to mention the fact that it has been involved in some film festivals this year, including the New York Film Festival and the Mill Valley Film Festival this month. 

For those of you unfamiliar with The Secret Life of Walter Mitty, it centres around an office worker, who combines romancing his co-worker, with his life in a fantasy world. When he learns that both he and the woman he loves are in danger of losing their jobs, he heads off on a global trip to put things right. 

Kristen Wiig is also in the movie 

The Secret Life of Walter Mitty has an impressive cast, which includes the likes of Ben Stiller (who also directs and produces the movie), Kristen Wiig, Adam Scott, Sean Penn, Kathryn Hahnand Patton Oswalt. The Secret Life of Walter Mitty opens on December 25 in the US and then on December 26 in the UK.</content> 
